quran[18]{c,v,t}:
  68,43,"Tsimoni tsiabu tsilihenga hasi, tsisoni tsilibalia muno, toto bwene balaangungwa okhurerera Nyasaye obweni bwabu hasi (nibali khushialo) nibali abalamu muno."
  68,44,"Kho ndeshela balia bakatsulanga likhuwa lino, khulabasitia khushinyasio kalahakalaha munjila yabalamanyile tawe."
  68,45,"Ne ndalabahelesia ebise. Toto amaraba kanje ni amasiro."
  68,46,"Nohomba obasabanga omurungo, nabo bakhayungwa eshichelo esho khulwa neeshisiro?"
  68,47,"Nohoma bali nende kefisa kabahandikanga?"
  68,48,"Kho linda okhula shinga Nyasaye wuwo Omulesi yetsa okhubusia eshina, ne olaba ta shinga omundu weyimonye (omurumwa Yunus) tawe, olwa yalaanga nafwinyiikhe."
  68,49,"Tsikhayanga okhumuulila tsimbabaasi okhurula khu Nyasaye wuwe Omulesi, yakhasalilwe khulukuku nafunanibwa."
  68,50,"Halali Nyasaye wuwe Omulesi namwawula, mana namukhola okhuba mubandu abalayi."
  68,51,"Ne abakhayi bali hambi muno okhukhureresia khu tsimoni tsiabu, olwa bawulila ametsulisio ka Nyasaye. Ne baboolanga mbu: “Toto bwene ye ni omulalu.”"
  68,52,"Ne amakhuwa kano (Ikurani) shikali halali ni ametsulisio khubiloonje bioosi."
  69,1,"Eliatoto (lilirurila)."
  69,2,"Ne eliatoto (lilirurila) elo ni shina?"
  69,3,"Ne nishina shikhumanyia eliatoto elo?"
  69,4,"Abandu ba Tsamudi nende A’ad bakatsula amasila karenjinjia omwoyo."
  69,5,"Mana Abandu ba Tsamudi basishibwa nende amasila amakali."
  69,6,"Ne Abandu ba A’ad basishibwa nomuyeka kweyimbumbuyeka."
  69,7,"Okwayabarumila khubilo saba nende tsinyanga munane tsilondokhana, olola Abandu nibalambalile shinga emisala chia mitende emikhaya."
  69,8,"Kho ololangakhwo yesiyesi mubo watong’a?"